(4667, 727, 'First prepare the Cacik: For the Cacik: Chop the cucumber into tiny pieces, as small as you can, and place in a bowl. Cover the cucumber with salt and set aside for 30 minutes. The cucumbers will start to exude their juices which will flavour the yogurt nicely.', 1, '2023-04-25 06:24:56', '2023-04-25 06:24:56'),
(4668, 727, 'Put a griddle pan on medium  high heat, cover the peppers with olive oil and start to char.', 2, '2023-04-25 06:24:56', '2023-04-25 06:24:56'),
(4669, 727, 'Cut the tomato and cucumber into medium pieces. Slice the red onion as thin as you can. Chop the parsley fine.', 3, '2023-04-25 06:24:56', '2023-04-25 06:24:56'),
(4670, 727, 'Place all ingredients in a bowl and cover with a the juice of 1 lemon. Season with salt and pepper.', 4, '2023-04-25 06:24:56', '2023-04-25 06:24:56'),
