(5713, 873, 'Preheat oven to 450 degrees.Rinse and pat dry each piece of chicken, making sure it is well-dried. Trim off all the fat or loose pieces of meat.', 1, '2023-04-25 06:26:36', '2023-04-25 06:26:36'),
