(7622, 1150, 'Heat 2 Tbsp olive in in a large pot over medium heat.', 5, '2023-04-25 06:32:58', '2023-04-25 06:32:58'),
(7623, 1150, 'Add onion and garlic and saute until softened, 5 to 8 minutes.', 6, '2023-04-25 06:32:58', '2023-04-25 06:32:58'),
(7624, 1150, 'Add ground turkey and heat until cooked through, breaking up into pieces and stirring occasionally as it cooks. Season with salt and pepper. Once cooked, add chili powder, chipotle peppers, jalapeno and poblano peppers, and adobo sauce. Stir to combine then add chicken stock, beans, and tomatoes. Cover, reduce heat to low, and let cook at least 1 to 2 hours, stirring ocassionally. Season with salt, pepper, and chili powder to taste before serving.', 7, '2023-04-25 06:32:58', '2023-04-25 06:32:58'),
