(7843, 1187, 'Add the cooked macaroni to the saucepot with the sauting spinach and toss add the processed cottage cheese mixture and toss. Turn off heat. Top with the remaining 4 oz. of cheddar cheese. Cover and let the cheddar cheese melt. This takes only a second or two.', 4, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
