(7867, 1194, 'Cook the pasta according to packet instructions (in salted water).Meanwhile: grate the Parmesan cheese and set aside.Once the pasta is ready, drain the water and pour over extra virgin olive oil. Throw in grated cheese, sprinkle with chili flakes and mix well.', 1, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
