(7870, 1195, 'Add the onion and saute until it\'s soft and translucent, about 10 minutes.  (Try not to let the onion brown...turn down the heat if you have to.)Toss in the minced garlic and cook for another 4 minutes or so.', 2, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
