(7892, 1197, 'Clean core and leaves from cauliflower (you do not have to have any precision when doing this).  Chop cauliflower into pieces.  Pieces should be roughly 1/2\" - 3/4\".', 3, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
