(7900, 1197, 'In another large saucepan, over medium high heat, melt 3 tablespoons of butter.  Once melted, whisk in flour.  Keep whisking to ensure that there are no lumps.  After 5-7 minutes, the butter and flour mixture should be a light caramel color.', 11, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
(7901, 1197, 'Add the soy milk, bay leaves, paprika, lemon juice, thyme, garlic powder and Szechuan pepper.  Stir occasionally for 10 - 15 minutes.  The mixture should thicken up.', 12, '2023-04-25 06:32:59', '2023-04-25 06:32:59'),
